one machine for each system => one machine for multiple virtual system

SYSTEM virtualized structure 
-host system
-guest system  										docker
having multiple equals guest system can be avoided using only one docker.
-virtual machine									containers(lightweight virtual machine)

METHOD
-host machine
-install docker
-install container

N.B.: remember to delete images and container not used or stoped

DOCKERFILE: file that docker use as configuration when building the container

NOTE
-can map a local directory to a container
-keep docker and containers update!!

UDOCKER
docker software to run container without privilegs

ES.: 
DOCKER COMPOSE
create 2 container, one expose a website the other contain the data of it(hidden)
-YML file: configure docker compose
-can attach docker container to it 
-work only on one machine
